            <div id="home" class="page-content-item active" data-title="Analytext | Free Financial Textual Data for AI & Research" data-description="Accelerate your financial and accounting research with Analytext's public repository of pre-parsed textual data from SEC filings (10-K, 10-Q), including MD&A, Risk Factors, and financial notes.">
                <section class="text-center">
                     <div class="hero-bg rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden mb-20 px-8 py-20">
                        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Unlock Insights from Financial Texts</h1>
                        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto">A public repository of parsed textual data from SEC filings, including major sections and financial statement notes from 10-K and 10-Q reports, designed to accelerate business research.</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-blue-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                            Based on the paper: Codesso, M., Hoitash, R., & Hoitash, U. (2025). 
                            <a href="https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=5212626" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-white hover:underline">
                                Textual Financial Data Repository and Python Code for Machine Learning, Al, and Textual Analyses.
                            </a>
                        </p>
                         <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center gap-x-6">
                            <a href="#" data-page="secFilings" class="nav-link-button rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-blue-600 shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-50">Get Data</a>
